<div class="process-timeline">
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">1</div>
<h3>Discovery & Assessment</h3>
<p>We begin with a comprehensive assessment of your business, challenges, and opportunities through stakeholder interviews, data analysis, and operational review.</p>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">2</div>
<h3>Strategy Development</h3>
<p>Based on our findings, we develop customized strategies and recommendations tailored to your specific goals, resources, and market conditions.</p>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">3</div>
<h3>Implementation Planning</h3>
<p>We create detailed implementation roadmaps with clear milestones, responsibilities, and success metrics to ensure effective execution.</p>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">4</div>
<h3>Execution Support</h3>
<p>We work alongside your team to implement changes, providing hands-on support, training, and guidance throughout the transformation.</p>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">5</div>
<h3>Performance Monitoring</h3>
<p>We establish KPIs and monitoring systems to track progress, measure results, and make adjustments to ensure sustainable success.</p>
